## Commands

# Sum-Constrained Permutations:
|+ ''rep_sum_permutations''      | ''rep_sum_permutation_index2list''        | ''rep_sum_permutation_list2index''
| ''rep_total_sum_permutations'' | ''rep_total_sum_permutation_index2list''  | ''rep_total_sum_permutation_list2index''

